  %% Diagram 37: Request Security Defense-in-Depth Pipeline

  In[Incoming Request]
  TLS[HTTPS/TLS + Edge WAF]
  CORS[CORS Origin Validation]
  Rate[Rate Limiter\nauth/checkout/AI tier]
  DTO[DTO Validation + Sanitization]
  SQL[Parameterized DB Access]
  AuthZ[RBAC + Domain Authorization]
  Handler[Application Handler]

  Reject401[401 Unauthorized]
  Reject403[403 Forbidden]
  Reject429[429 Too Many Requests]
  Reject400[400 Bad Request]

  In --> TLS --> CORS --> Rate --> DTO --> SQL --> AuthZ --> Handler

  CORS -->|Invalid origin| Reject403
  Rate -->|Limit exceeded| Reject429
  DTO -->|Invalid payload| Reject400
  AuthZ -->|No permission| Reject403
  TLS -->|Auth missing/invalid| Reject401
